Louis AVENA and Earl Webb, Appellants, v. UNITED STATES OF AMERICA, Appellee. No. 6164. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit June 9, 1930.

Before RUDKIN, DIETRICH, and WILBUR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
